trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.CPU1.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.CPU2.temp.last()}>70
trigger.name: CPU temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMA.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMB.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMC.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMD.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEME.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMF.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMG.temp.last()}>70 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.MEMH.temp.last()}>70
trigger.name: DIMM temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.PSU1Power.last()}<1 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.PSU2Power.last()}<1
trigger.name: Power supply issue on {HOSTNAME}

trigger.expression: {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.Systemboard1.temp.last()}>50 or {Fujitsu PRIMERGY RX350 S7:ipmi.Systemboard2.temp.last()}>50
trigger.name: System temperature critical on {HOSTNAME}
